# Install WSUS role\nInstall-WindowsFeature -Name UpdateServices, UpdateServices-UI, UpdateServices-RSAT\n\n# Post-installation tasks\nInvoke-WsusServerConfigurationWizard\n\n# Configure Group Policy\n# Open Group Policy Management Console (gpmc.msc) and configure the following settings:\n# Computer Configuration -> Administrative Templates -> Windows Components -> Windows Update\n# - Specify Intranet Microsoft update service location: http://<WSUSServer>:8530\n# - Enable client-side targeting\n# - Configure automatic updates\n\n# Approve updates\n# Open WSUS Management Console (wsus.msc), navigate to 'Updates', select updates, and click 'Approve'.\n\n# Generate reports\n# In WSUS Management Console, navigate to 'Reports' to create compliance reports.